Author: summerservice
Text: thank you. i’m on week 5 now and I’ve been feeling this for most of it, so the dr. only wants to give it a couple more weeks before we make any changes. hopeful things will get better!

Author: mrsnoire
Text: you have to give it the necessary time to make sure that it is working as it should, the first weeks or even months you may have unpleasant symptoms, but once your brain and sertraline (or any psychotropic medication) achieve a balance in your neurotransmitters, these symptoms will disappear progressively. Give your treatment a chance to work for you and your mental well-being. I hope you feel better with time.
